      "message": "Unfortunately the term VNF Package has been used loosely through the document.  I don't think it's been firmly established that a VNF package always equates to a CSAR.  As it stands, a VNF can be packaged as an archive of Heat files or a CSAR.  Perhaps we add a qualifier such as The VNF or PNF CSAR Package **MUST** be arranged as specified in TOSCA Simple Profile in YAML 1.2.",
